Package: indicoio
Title: A simple R Wrapper for the indico set of APIs - http://indico.io
Version: 0.1
Author: Alexander Gedranovich <gedranovich@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Alexander Gedranovich <gedranovich@gmail.com>
Description: R-based client for Machine Learning APIs at http://indico.io.
    Provides wrappers for following APIs: Positive/Negative Sentiment Analysis,
    Political Sentiment Analysis, Image Feature Extraction, Facial Emotion
    Recognition, Facial Feature Extraction, Language Detection
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.2),
    httr,
    rjson,
    stringr
License: MIT
LazyData: true
Suggests:
    testthat
